<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB04790</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT AMENDING CERTAIN SECTIONS OF REPUBLIC ACT NO. 9184, OTHERWISE KNOWN AS THE GOVERNMENT PROCUREMENT REFORM ACT</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Provides amendments to the following sections, among others as follows: 1) Sec.18 - ... Reference to brand names shall not be allowed; PROVIDED, THAT REFERENCE TO BRAND NAMES CAN BE MADE BY PROCURING ENTITIES WHICH ARE CONSTITUTED PRIMARILY FOR PROPRIETARY OR BUSINESS FUNCTION; 2) Sec.32 - Bid for the Procurement of Goods, Infrastructure Projects AND LEASE OF REAL PROPERTY...; 3) Sec.50 - provides additional condition when direct contracting may be resorted to such as d) FOOD, BEVERAGE AND HOTEL ACCOMMODATIONS, WHEN THE PROCURING ENTITY IS A GOCCs ENGAGED PRIMARILY IN PROPRIETARY OR BUSINESS FUNCTIONS SUCH AS ENTERTAINMENT AND GAMING INDUSTRY; 4) Sec.51 - also provides for additional condition when repeat order may be allowed: IN CASE OF PROCUREMENT OF RAW AND PERSIHABLE GOODS AND COMMODITIES, PRICE INCREASE SHALL NOT EXCEED 25% OF THE ORIGINAL CONTRACT.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>MACAPAGAL ARROYO, GLORIA</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2017-01-18</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Bravo (M.) (088 2017-05-10)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>COMMITEE HEARINGS/ACTIONS:</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp1. Scheduled for meeting/hearing on 2017-03-07</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp2. Under deliberation by the Mother Committee on 2017-03-07</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON APPROPRIATIONS ON 2017-01-24</td></tr></table>